1
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,310
Mr. Lu.

2
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,780
Did you call me for something?

3
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,150
Nothing much.

4
00:01:34,590 --> 00:01:35,710
Let's talk later.

5
00:01:37,039 --> 00:01:38,039
Call them all up.

6
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:51,490
-Hello, Mr. Lu.
-Hello, Mr. Lu.

7
00:01:53,310 --> 00:01:55,950
Mr. Xiao, I know you
never come to a place like this.

8
00:01:55,950 --> 00:01:58,009
There's a first time for everything.

9
00:01:59,070 --> 00:01:59,840
Pick one.

10
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:05,900
Not satisfied?

11
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:10,080
Change to another group.

12
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,079
This suits your status.

13
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,360
Look at her waist.

14
00:02:41,630 --> 00:02:42,520
Her figure.

15
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:50,280
Satisfied, Mr. Xiao?

16
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:58,280
I'm really curious
about your relationship.

17
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:02,590
Lovers?

18
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,000
Friends?

19
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,010
Have you slept with her?

20
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:23,710
You haven't slept with her, I guess.

21
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:24,840
Alright.

22
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,760
She's yours tonight.

23
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:30,520
Remember,

24
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:32,250
just for one night.

25
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,590
No need.

26
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,660
Aren't you taking your stuff?

27
00:03:49,430 --> 00:03:50,190
Go with him.

28
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:54,680
I told you to go with him.

29
00:04:05,470 --> 00:04:06,730
Putting on an act, huh?

30
00:04:07,910 --> 00:04:08,750
Is it here?

31
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,530
Are you going or not?

32
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:22,800
Since you hate her so much,

33
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,720
I'll help you.

34
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,020
Look at the scar on her arm.

35
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:29,120
Do you know who exactly

36
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,920
took that stab for you back then?

37
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,240
How...

38
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:34,730
how do you know about this?

39
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:39,000
You are weak.

40
00:04:39,950 --> 00:04:42,280
You don't even dare
to face your own heart.

41
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:45,280
First ask yourself
whether it's love or hate.

42
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:51,290
You don't deserve to fight me.

43
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,280
Who allowed you to come here?

44
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,510
What?

45
00:06:37,830 --> 00:06:39,390
Are you going to punish me again?

46
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:41,360
Here or somewhere else?

47
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,600
Let me tell you.

48
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,950
You are mine.

49
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,480
You must obey my orders.

50
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,830
How did you know?

51
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:34,350
This is my greatest trophy
in over 20 years.

52
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,600
How could I not know?

53
00:07:43,270 --> 00:07:44,270
So,

54
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:46,680
you knew all along

55
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,940
that I was going to propose to you, right?

56
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:52,830
But you didn't say a word!

57
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:57,600
You could have at least said goodbye,

58
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,360
or

59
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,770
you could have kept lying to me.

60
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:05,040
You turned a blind eye.

61
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,810
What did you take me for?

62
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,480
A pawn?

63
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:12,510
Just a pawn on your path to revenge?

64
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:17,270
I looked for you for 3 years.

65
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:19,510
I suffered for 3 years!

66
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,830
Su Xia.

67
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,750
You owe me.

68
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,260
You will pay me back with your whole life.

69
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:36,760
Don't even think about
running away in this life.

70
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,630
Lu Fan.

71
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,550
Do you really think my father's grave

72
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:49,720
and a few photos

73
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:51,360
can make me surrender and obey you,

74
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:54,290
allowing you to endlessly
humiliate and torture me?

75
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,930
I don't owe you anymore.

76
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:04,760
Those are your mother's ashes.

77
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,670
We are even.

78
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:15,870
Su Xia.

79
00:09:21,270 --> 00:09:22,480
If one day,

80
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:25,000
we can truly forget

81
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,860
the pain we brought to each other,

82
00:09:28,390 --> 00:09:29,600
let's meet again.

83
00:10:43,670 --> 00:10:45,600
It seems he can't bear to let you go.

84
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:48,640
He even chased after you to see you off.

85
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:54,080
Could it be that he can't live without you
for the rest of his life?

86
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:09,910
Good.

87
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,630
Good, very good.

88
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:18,290
This is the perfect match
I've found for my daughter.

89
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:22,960
Has Lu Fan been tangling

90
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,840
with that woman surnamed Su recently?

91
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,600
Yes.

92
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,270
Notify the Business Department.

93
00:11:27,270 --> 00:11:29,240
I want to see
the basic project plan tomorrow.

94
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:29,960
Tomorrow, with Lu Fan—

95
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:30,480
Jian Xi.

96
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:34,370
What have you been busy with recently?

97
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,670
Why did Lu Fan reject

98
00:11:36,670 --> 00:11:38,440
our cooperation proposal again?

99
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:40,440
I told you to go to him for marriage,

100
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,360
not to be his assistant!

101
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,840
You have no brains at all.

102
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,520
I raised you for nothing!

103
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,890
I have my own arrangements.

104
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,270
Go tell those people,

105
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,980
in 3 days at the latest,

106
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,600
I want that woman gone.

107
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,390
Hey, Xiao Qi.

108
00:12:10,550 --> 00:12:12,120
Could you send me
the address of the little girl

109
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,080
receiving at-home treatment

110
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,150
for depression again?

111
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:15,410
I can't seem to find it.

112
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:17,630
Okay.

113
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:31,000
Are you following orders,
or do you just want money?

114
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,510
If it's money, I can pay double.

115
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,000
Ms. Su,

116
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:37,950
unfortunately,
they specifically want you dead.

117
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,150
Otherwise,

118
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,890
I would love to cooperate with you.

119
00:12:45,910 --> 00:12:47,600
After I have some fun with you,

120
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:49,390
it won't be too late to kill you.

121
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:54,840
-Boss!
-Boss!

122
00:12:55,790 --> 00:12:56,510
Boss!

123
00:12:59,870 --> 00:13:01,630
This witch is ruthless.

124
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:04,750
Brothers, let's take her together!

125
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,360
I think this one is pretty.

126
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:15,760
I'll definitely
look like a princess in it.

127
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:16,840
Look.

128
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:18,150
What do you think?

129
00:13:19,910 --> 00:13:20,720
Or this one.

130
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:26,000
-Hello?
-Mr. Lu,

131
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:28,140
Ms. Su Xia's location signal is gone.

132
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:30,390
What?

133
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:34,720
Okay, I'll be right there.

134
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,150
Lu Fan.

135
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:39,160
The wedding dress designer
is waiting for us.

136
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:43,330
I'm sorry. Something urgent came up.

137
00:13:44,270 --> 00:13:46,000
I'll let Qin Huai stay with you.

138
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:47,230
Take good care of her.

139
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:50,680
What's the point of him staying with me?

140
00:14:05,670 --> 00:14:06,720
Su,

141
00:14:06,910 --> 00:14:08,370
aren't you a good fighter?

142
00:14:20,790 --> 00:14:21,510
Run!

143
00:14:21,910 --> 00:14:22,510
Go!

144
00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:37,360
Su Xia.

145
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,510
Su Xia, are you okay?

146
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:41,960
Brother.

147
00:14:44,910 --> 00:14:45,550
Su Xia.

148
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,800
So it's you guys, huh?

149
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:41,750
The bleeding has stopped.

150
00:15:41,750 --> 00:15:42,630
It triggered her old injury.

151
00:15:42,630 --> 00:15:44,150
She needs surgery immediately.

152
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:46,950
Otherwise, the consequences
will be disastrous.

153
00:15:49,870 --> 00:15:51,270
What are you waiting for?

154
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:53,960
The surgery is too difficult.

155
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:55,320
None of our doctors...

156
00:15:57,030 --> 00:15:58,000
Useless!

157
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:06,670
Su Xia's arm has always been treated

158
00:16:06,670 --> 00:16:09,080
by the foreign expert I found for her.

159
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:10,910
Mr. Lu,

160
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:13,980
you really made things worse.

161
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:16,750
Get out.

162
00:16:18,910 --> 00:16:20,150
Get Dr. Li for me.

163
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:21,440
Right now.

164
00:16:22,030 --> 00:16:23,550
I care about her life,

165
00:16:24,270 --> 00:16:25,670
not necessarily her arm.

166
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:28,790
If you don't let her go,

167
00:16:29,630 --> 00:16:30,760
I can afford to wait.

168
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:41,150
Xiao Qi.

169
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:44,700
I must take her away today.

170
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,750
Just try and take her away.

171
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:49,010
What if I insist on taking her away today?

172
00:16:49,030 --> 00:16:50,120
Try it.

173
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,200
You want to fight?

174
00:16:53,030 --> 00:16:53,840
Let me go.

175
00:16:56,270 --> 00:16:57,930
You have to come with me today.

176
00:16:58,480 --> 00:16:59,510
Am I clear?

177
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:04,030
I'll say it again. Let me go!

178
00:17:12,829 --> 00:17:13,960
I told you,

179
00:17:14,680 --> 00:17:17,069
you have to come with me today.
